    <item>
      <title>印度家庭预计未来几个月通胀将加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-coming-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行的一项调查显示，印度家庭预计未来三个月至一年内通胀将加速，主要受食品价格、住房和服务成本的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/indian-households-see-inflation-accelerating-in-coming-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥通胀率在利率决定前超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/mexico-inflation-overshoots-forecast-ahead-of-rate-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥七月份的整体通胀率略高于预期，这增加了央行在周四晚些时候举行的第三次会议上维持关键利率不变的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/mexico-inflation-overshoots-forecast-ahead-of-rate-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:11:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
